4 and 5 at Duke Energy Florida;
• a $312 million increase in operation, maintenance and other expense primarily due to higher costs related to storms, vegetation management
costs and severance charges; and
• a $26 million increase in property and other taxes primarily due to higher revenue related taxes at Duke Energy Florida.
