respects, the financial position of the Company as of December 31, 2018 and 2017, and the results of its operations and its cash flows for each of the
three years in the periods ended December 31, 2018, December 31, 2017, October 31, 2016, and for the two months ended December 31, 2016, in
conformity with accounting principles generally accepted in the United States of America.
