The following table shows information as of December 31, 2018, about securities to be issued upon exercise of outstanding options, warrants and rights
under Duke Energy's equity compensation plans, along with the weighted-average exercise price of the outstanding options, warrants and rights and the
number of securities remaining available for future issuance under the plans.
